		   <tr><td class="headerrow" colspan="2"><a name="113095456018117"></a><span class="msgSubject">Blue diamonds</span><br clear="all" />
		   <span class="sm">Posted: Nov  2nd  2005 at  1:53pm EDT<span class="notbold">| <span class="sm">IP: Logged</span> | <a class="sm" href="/db/item.html?item=14483;mid=113095456018117#post"><img src="/shared/reply_to_thread_ico.gif" border="0" alt="Reply..." height="11" width="17" /> Reply to this</a> </span></span></td></tr>
		   <tr><td valign="top" class="mform" ><span class="fs8"><span class="notbold">By: </span><a href="/db/poster.html?user=4332"><span class="Scholar">Palladia</span></a><b><span class="Scholar"><br/>Scholar</span></b>
