<p>Remember that there is a Wisdom/Int/Str component in combines (depends on class) that you need to get over 190 for the maximum chance of success. So even though a twink lvl 1 druid can max tailoring, be sure to twink him for his main attribute as well. This was Verdant's way of making the halfling more popular...</p>
